586
00:31:28,350 --> 00:31:29,620
Oh, boy.

587
00:31:30,800 --> 00:31:32,770
Kanun, give him a lesson.

588
00:31:34,100 --> 00:31:35,760
Pat, you're still young.

589
00:31:36,220 --> 00:31:37,970
